description.p:
One example of a suitable medium for use in the present invention includes:
com steep water corresponding to about 30 to about 45 g/L steep water dry solids;
about 80 to about 120 g/L glucose, fructose or a mixture thereof;
about 0 to about 10 g/L yeast extract;
about 0 to about 1 g/L of a nonionic surfactant such as TweenR 80;
about 0 to about 2 g/L potassium hydrogen phosphate (K2HPO4);
about 0 to about 0.2 g/L magnesium sulfate (MgSO4);
about 0 to about 0.05 g/L manganese sulfate (MnSO4);
about 0 to about 2 g/L ammonium citrate; and
optionally, about 10 to about 50 g/L calcium carbonate (CaCO3).
